    • Field Detail

      • transactionId

        public java.lang.String transactionId
        This contains information that was retrieved for the passed criteria. The transactionId gives a unique handle to the data. This must be passed to the API as the input parameter lastTransactionId in subsequent calls, if you wish to retrieve more unprocessed records without marking the current trigger (transaction id) as processed.

      • xmlImportData

        public java.lang.String xmlImportData
        XML data as published for the requested transaction.

      • shipNode

        public java.lang.String shipNode
        Ship node for which data was retrieved.

      • transactionType

        public java.lang.String transactionType
        Unique identifier for a particular interface. For example, ship confirm transaction has a value of "AD".
